# Communication And Verification

- Communicate progress briefly during substantial work.
- Explain what changed, why it changed, and where it changed.
- Validate changes using configured project commands from `docs/stack-configuration.md`.
- Prefer `LINT_COMMAND`, `TEST_COMMAND`, and `BUILD_COMMAND` placeholders over stack-specific assumptions.
- If validation cannot run, explain what was not verified and how to verify locally.
